high_descs: Turn left to the sofa just ahead.
Pick up the butter knife on the sofa.
Slice the tomato on the sofa.
Turn right and go straight ahead to the far corner of the room with the microwave.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Return to the sliced tomato on the sofa.
Pick up one tomato slice.
Go back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice into the microwave.
Turn right to the fridge ahead.
Remove the tomato from the fridge.
Go back to the microwave.
Put the whole tomato in the microwave.
Pick up the butter knife you put in the microwave earlier.
Slice the whole tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a whole sliced tomato and one additional slice in a microwave.
